text: Euphlyctis ghoshi (Manipur frog, Ghosh's frog) is a species of frog found in Manipur, India. It is only known from its type locality in Khugairk Reserve Forest, Manipur. ==References== ghoshi Category:Frogs of India Category:Endemic fauna of Manipur Category:Amphibians described in 1991
title: Euphlyctis ghoshi
